CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 5, 1946, pg. 8 reads: "Double Ring Ceremony - Charming Miss Rosetta Austin, daughter of Edward Austin Sr., was united in marriage Sept. 24 with Hardine Moore, son of Mrs. Hardine Moore of Lynchburg, Va., in a ceremony held in home of Mr. and Mrs. George Austin. The Rev. J.B. Campbell officiated. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Rosetta Austin Moore wearing long sleeved gown with sheer yoke and sweetheart neckline, posed holding bouquet in home of Mr. and Mrs. George Austin
